1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 25=

21
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:32,560
- Your Ladyship.
- Don't be nervous.

22
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,400
- Your Ladyship.
- Come.

23
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,040
- Your Ladyship, don't be afraid.
- Come on.

24
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:36,200
Push, Your Ladyship!

25
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,120
Push hard!

26
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,120
Keep pushing.

27
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,400
- Your Ladyship.
- Don't give up.

28
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,240
Your Ladyship, don't be afraid.

29
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,070
Your Ladyship, keep going.

30
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:42,920
Your Ladyship.

31
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,870
- Push, Your Ladyship.
- Your Ladyship.

32
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,840
Push, Your Ladyship.

33
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,230
Come on, push harder.

34
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,070
Almost, Your Ladyship.

35
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,590
Almost, almost.

36
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:50,510
Push, Your Ladyship.

37
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,590
Push, Your Ladyship.

38
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,550
Your Ladyship.

39
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,670
Your Ladyship.

40
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:55,630
Come on.

41
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:56,640
- Push.
- Your Ladyship.

42
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,480
Your Ladyship, almost there.

43
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,430
I can see the head.

44
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,590
The head is out, Your Ladyship.

45
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,320
Ye Jin.

46
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,320
Ye Jin.

47
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:05,350
Ye Jin.

48
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,230
Are you alright?

49
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:08,790
Ye Jin.

50
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:10,870
Your Highness.

51
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,840
I have to go back to my world.

52
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:17,000
Don't be too sad.

53
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,590
No.

54
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:20,550
Don't go.

55
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,870
Don't leave me behind.

56
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,560
Stay with me.

57
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,190
Stay with me.

58
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,280
Your Highness.

59
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,240
Coming here and meeting you.

60
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:31,400
I don't regret it at all.

61
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,520
I don't want to leave either.

62
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,840
But my time is up.

63
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,870
I want you to know

64
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,120
my name is Shen Zhaodi.

65
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:42,430
I am twenty-five.

66
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,000
I never had a crush before.

67
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,590
You're my first boyfriend.

68
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,190
If there is a next life,

69
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:51,360
I will surely marry you.

70
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,200
Alright.

71
00:02:52,330 --> 00:02:53,680
We'll stay together till old age.

72
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,240
- Alright?
- Alright.

73
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,960
Your Majesty.

74
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,310
Your Majesty, the ancestral rule says

75
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:00,870
no man may enter the birthing chamber.

76
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:03,120
Let alone you, Your Majesty.

77
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,430
Concubine Hui is blessed by fate.

78
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,960
Mother and child will be fine.

79
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,680
I thought Consort De
could handle palace affairs.

80
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,240
I never thought she'd be so useless

81
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,630
as to make such a grave mistake!

82
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,280
She's not just foolish,

83
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,000
but greedy as well.

84
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,430
Sixi, draft the edict.

85
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:21,910
Consort De is arrogant.

86
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,310
And she broke palace rules.

87
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:24,800
Strip her of her title.

88
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,910
Revoke her power over the harem!

89
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,400
Yes, Your Majesty.

90
00:03:28,850 --> 00:03:30,150
- Your Ladyship.
- Push, Your Ladyship!

91
00:03:30,490 --> 00:03:31,560
Almost there, almost there!

92
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:32,870
Push, push!

93
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,150
Don't lose strength, Your Ladyship.

94
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,470
Harder!

95
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,590
Almost there, Your Ladyship!

96
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,030
Harder!

97
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,590
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

98
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,080
The Crown Prince is born.

99
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,150
Mother and child are safe.

100
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,400
Your Majesty.

101
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,240
General Gui won the war.

102
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,080
The southwest battle is a great victory!

103
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,540
A great victory.

104
00:03:58,630 --> 00:03:59,710
What a great victory!

105
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,150
This is a divine blessing!

106
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:05,240
The Crown Prince truly brings me luck.

107
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,400
Convey my decree.

108
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,750
General Gui has great merit.

109
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,960
He is appointed
General of the Southern Pacification.

110
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,680
Give him ten thousand taels of silver.

111
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,520
Grant him a mansion and land.

112
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,870
To honor his achievements.

113
00:04:18,270 --> 00:04:19,510
My Crown Prince.

114
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,950
His nickname is Xiangrui.

115
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,390
Don't leave.

116
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,370
Miss Ye Jin,

117
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:28,220
time to take the medicine.

118
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,430
I'm dying.

119
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,040
Why take medicine?

120
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,430
Physician Zhang said,

121
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,950
the dagger was off by an inch.

122
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,190
It looks serious.

123
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,800
But it's not fatal.

124
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,240
Forget the next life.

125
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:43,910
This life

126
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,390
isn't over yet.

127
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,560
Take the medicine.

128
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,070
(My secret is fully exposed.)

129
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,120
(Oh my God.)

130
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:55,360
Your Majesty.

131
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,080
Hui.

132
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,080
Hui.

133
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,270
Don't hold on.

134
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,070
I'm here to see you.

135
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:09,750
Your Majesty.

136
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,430
Rest well.

137
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,830
When you're better.

138
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:14,870
I'll give you the proper title

139
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:15,950
and all the honors.

140
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,750
Your Majesty's grace is overwhelming.

141
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:21,800
I don't deserve it.

142
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,480
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

143
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,240
I...

144
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,510
am not from the Niohuru clan.

145
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:44,680
I'm Yun Hui, daughter of
Prefect of Huzhou Yun Tianci.

146
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:49,600
My father was honest all his life.

147
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,070
He was loyal to you.

148
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,240
Yet treacherous courtiers framed him

149
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,430
and he was murdered brutally.

150
00:05:56,510 --> 00:05:57,870
Today, I

151
00:05:58,270 --> 00:06:00,240
want to seek justice for my father.

152
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:11,040
Speak slowly, my dear.

153
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,110
I'm listening.

154
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,040
It happened ten years ago.

155
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,720
To clear my father's name

156
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,600
and expose the Lan clan's crimes,

157
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:25,720
I've collected evidence secretly
for years.

158
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,240
It's all written in
these blood petitions.

159
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,310
These are the eighteen crimes
of the Lan clan.

160
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:33,070
Every one is shocking.

161
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,920
I swear with my life

162
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,680
that all this is true.

163
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,480
All these years,

164
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:54,950
I was deceived by the Lan clan's lies.

165
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,750
I didn't know how evil they were.

166
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,870
If I don't eliminate them,

167
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,120
the realm won't be peaceful

168
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,190
and the people won't live in safety.

169
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,800
Your blood petitions
arrived just in time.

170
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,030
Sixi.

171
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:17,830
Issue my decree.

172
00:07:18,130 --> 00:07:19,600
Fully investigate the Lan clan's crimes

173
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:23,070
Leave nothing unexamined.

174
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:34,680
By the Emperor's divine order,

175
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:39,270
Concubine Hui,
Zhi Hui of the Niohuru clan,

176
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:41,360
is virtuous and talented,

177
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,510
diligent and gentle,

178
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,750
gracious and pure,

179
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:48,070
kind in nature.

180
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:50,390
You greatly comfort my heart.

181
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:54,070
Thus, I order you to oversee the harem

182
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,310
and appoint you Empress.

183
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:00,160
(After this palace coup,)

184
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,480
(a new face took the throne.)

185
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,920
(Zhi Hui turned the tide)

186
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,960
(and rose to)

187
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:06,870
(become Empress overnight.)

188
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,750
(But what about me and the 14th Prince?)

189
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,600
(How long can we live in peace)

190
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:14,600
(in this deep palace?)

191
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,640
Your Highness.

192
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,800
Let's get married.

193
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:22,680
Is what you said

194
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:23,790
true?

195
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:24,790
Mm.

196
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,920
Then tomorrow
I will inform the Imperial Household

197
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,760
to prepare the wedding.

198
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,910
No need for a big ceremony.

199
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,670
In my world,

200
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:36,910
we just register,

201
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:37,840
exchange tokens

202
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,240
and we're married.

203
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:40,750
A token?

204
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,720
This jade pendant has been with me
since childhood.

205
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,320
I'll give it to you.

206
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,200
In my world,

207
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:58,270
a ring is the token.

208
00:08:58,630 --> 00:09:00,030
But I didn't prepare a man's ring.

209
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,270
So take this for now.

210
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,720
Miss Ye Jin.

211
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,000
Her Majesty

212
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,870
asks to see you alone.

213
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:31,870
Alright.

214
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,240
I'll be right back.

215
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,230
Mm.

216
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,960
Greetings, Your Majesty.

217
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,360
I wonder why Your Majesty

218
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,120
summoned me.

219
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,480
We're like sisters,
no need for formalities.

220
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:07,670
Call me Hui like before.

221
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:09,750
I dare not.

222
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,790
Between us,

223
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,440
we've grown distant after all.

224
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,480
Last night at the Zi hour,

225
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:23,600
Consort Lan was sent to the Cold Palace.

226
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,320
At dawn today,

227
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:28,080
the entire Lan clan was executed.

228
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,240
Our revenge

229
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,870
is finally done.

230
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:43,600
What will you do next?

231
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:47,670
I want to leave the palace
with the 14th Prince.

232
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:48,910
From now on,

233
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:50,510
I'll never interfere in harem affairs.

234
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,000
Leaving the palace is good.

235
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,870
The world is wide and free.

236
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,350
But...

237
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,200
I'm a little reluctant to part with you.

238
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,120
Your Majesty, you flatter me.

239
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:04,080
You're the Empress now,

240
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,480
with a firm position

241
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:09,270
and the Crown Prince by your side.

242
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,670
Even without me,

243
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:14,240
no one will challenge you in the palace.

244
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:34,630
This toast is to see you off.

245
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,630
And to thank you

246
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,870
for helping me through hard times.

247
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,960
Your Majesty, I accept

248
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:45,840
your kindness.

249
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,320
Fine wine.

250
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:28,940
(Shen Clan Clinic)

251
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,200
I'm back.

252
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:44,180
(Fan Support Report, Treasure Boy)

253
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:51,630
Was everything just a dream?

254
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:03,260
("Once an Empress")

255
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:06,350
No.

256
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,150
Ye Jin died
in the first few pages already.

257
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,120
Why is there more?

258
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:55,100
(Shen Clan Clinic)

259
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:00,590
Ye Jin.

260
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:02,710
Ye Jin.

261
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,350
Ye Jin?

262
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:21,080
♪I am but an outsider♪

263
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:23,280
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

264
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:27,560
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

265
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:31,800
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

266
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:39,320
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

267
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:42,880
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

268
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:45,400
♪I know how this story ends♪

269
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:49,960
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

270
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:54,400
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

271
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:02,680
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

272
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:05,960
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

273
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:09,240
♪A history that no one can search♪

274
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:12,760
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

275
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:14,560
♪I am but an outsider♪

276
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:16,800
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

277
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:20,840
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

278
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:25,520
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

279
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:32,840
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

280
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:36,200
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

281
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,680
♪I know how this story ends♪

282
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:42,840
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

283
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:46,120
